{
  "id": "RAW_95d148",
  "title": "又一个 Deep Research 来了！1-2 分钟抵人类专家数小时，所有人免费",
  "url": "https://www.jiqizhixin.com/articles/2025-02-15-3",
  "date": "2025-02-15 11:57:59",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>Deep Research 又迎来一位新玩家。</p>\n  <p>就在刚刚，人工智能初创公司 Perplexity 上线 Deep Research 功能，其能生成任何主题的深度研究报告。</p>\n  <p>并且还对所有人免费开放 —— 非订阅用户每天可以执行最多 5 次查询，Pro 用户每天最多 500 次查询。</p>\n  <p>要知道 OpenAI Deep Research 需要每月 200 美元的订阅费。</p>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503471293\" data-ratio=\"0.715625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9d535b4a-73b6-4c5e-b328-497dcd1ff500/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"1\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ce182f2c-c69c-47d1-abef-09c0d16fb8d9/640.gif\" data-order=\"0\" alt=\"图片\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Perplexity Deep Research 为用户节省了数小时的时间。当用户提出一个 Deep Research 问题时，Perplexity 会执行数十次搜索，阅读数百个来源，并对材料进行推理，从而自主生成一份全面的报告。它在各种专家级任务中表现出色 —— 从金融、市场营销到产品研究 —— 并在「人类最后一次考试（Humanity’s Last Exam）」中取得了高水平的成绩。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   目前，Perplexity Deep Research 今天已在网页版上线，并很快上线 iOS、Android 和 Mac 平台。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   想要体验的用户，进入官网，在搜索框的模式选择器中选择 Deep Research，然后提交问题。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503471294\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e9cf8938-8d07-4d48-8e1f-5779d6790200/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"2\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/b9815b54-879d-43ad-b185-8ce68b6ef80a/640.gif\" data-order=\"1\" alt=\"图片\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   使用地址：https://www.perplexity.ai/?login-source=tryPro\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   在下面视频中，用户询问了这样一个问题：「使用所有可用的数据和估计，利润和现金流等行业标准，对美国 15 家最大的私营企业上市前的市值进行自下而上的估计……」Perplexity Deep Research 用时 2 分多钟生成了一份完整的报告。<img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/614d8599-a151-4bb1-8a2c-d0e22a2c9f2d/1739620499329.png\" style=\"width: 70%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\">Perplexity Deep Research 还可以对包括健康和技术在内的一系列复杂主题进行专家级分析。&nbsp;<img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/35fcd3c0-556d-4425-8770-54fe0ad95824/1739620517203.png\" style=\"width: 70%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\"><img src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/e26bdee0-1c94-48aa-8aa8-b07eb80d3302/1739620527215.png\" style=\"width: 70%;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>Perplexity Deep Research 是如何工作的？</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Perplexity 已经在回答问题方面表现出色。而 Deep Research 将问答功能提升到了一个新的高度，它只需花费 1-2 分钟即可完成人类专家需要数小时才能完成的工作。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   以下是它的工作原理：\n  </section>\n  <ul>\n   <li>\n    <section>\n     研究推理：配备了搜索和编码能力，Perplexity Deep Research 会迭代地进行搜索、阅读文档，并推理下一步该做什么，随着对主题领域的了解加深，不断优化研究计划。这类似于人类研究新话题的方式，在整个过程中逐步完善自己的理解；\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section>\n     报告撰写：一旦对资料来源进行了全面的评估，系统会将所有研究综合成一份清晰而全面的报告；\n    </section></li>\n   <li>\n    <section>\n     导出与分享：用户可以将最终报告导出为 PDF 或文档，或将其转换为 Perplexity 页面，与同事或朋友分享。\n    </section></li>\n  </ul>\n  <section>\n   <img data-imgfileid=\"503471295\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2d1b30d7-8edc-40f5-6123-cc2615d77f00/public\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" data-original-style=\"\" data-index=\"3\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/00d95861-5f91-4bc5-8f52-6ac712ced7be/640.gif\" data-order=\"2\" alt=\"图片\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471296\" data-ratio=\"0.8203703703703704\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/355227a1-37b7-41dd-6f32-5ffc0aad1e00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"4\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/75fcf93f-8a46-4a88-9396-5675ac90f292/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>何时使用 Deep Research</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Deep Research 旨在让每个人都能够对各种复杂主题进行专家级别的分析。目前，Deep Research 在金融、市场营销和技术等领域表现出色，同时在健康、产品研究和旅行规划等领域也同样实用。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   以下是一些可以在 Perplexity 上使用 Deep Research 的示例场景。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   金融：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471297\" data-ratio=\"1.3509259259259259\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/3d4c2cee-a983-4c58-a952-1298deea2700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"5\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/3db7ef9b-9d26-4374-9c59-90cc3c5aed6f/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   营销：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471298\" data-ratio=\"1.3509259259259259\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/e90277bb-dbe6-43fe-7b60-c239aa7dbd00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"6\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/a4ec4178-242d-425a-9333-bdb6a91fbe28/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   技术：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471299\" data-ratio=\"1.3509259259259259\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/92e64305-aa58-4db7-32ac-86fa9c30c300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"7\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/ba9da738-6236-4ded-b8eb-36518dbd1e18/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   旅游：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471300\" data-ratio=\"1.3509259259259259\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c14527ba-dc99-450f-f1bd-661271ef1500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"8\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/0da95971-90f5-4e78-91b6-bd187d515dc2/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <strong>超越 DeepSeek-R1 等顶级模型</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Perplexity Deep Research 在 SimpleQA 基准上的准确率达到了惊人的 93.9%，超过领先模型，如 o1 预览版。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471301\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/38c9b32e-d1ab-4321-83f2-23e22df64900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"9\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/2cfc7eac-c7c5-4149-b431-d20c120e4890/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   在「人类最后一次考试」中，Perplexity Deep Research 的得分为 21.1%，超过了 Gemini Thinking、o3-mini、o1、DeepSeek-R1 等顶级模型。但落后于 OpenAI Deep Research。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471302\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8e38825f-ab5a-4acb-dcaf-6c9ce612b800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"10\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/d08df36f-543e-4bd5-adfa-6e4403dc74ac/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   除了在行业基准测试中获得高分之外，Perplexity Deep Research 还能在不到 3 分钟的时间内完成大多数任务，并且 Perplexity 正在努力使其变得更快。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471303\" data-ratio=\"0.3972222222222222\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/7202c482-c980-4491-2e74-f7d03b6d7c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"11\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/77f6f018-53eb-4145-80b4-5d0f60453f4d/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   不过，网友试用后，对这个免费的功能并不看好，纷纷吐槽了起来：\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471304\" data-ratio=\"0.1557632398753894\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9fedf521-251c-45ca-c6ce-23cc7e897a00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"963\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"12\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/7b975fba-c0c4-4ebf-a79b-3e486e44e4c5/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471305\" data-ratio=\"0.34237995824634654\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10947fd8-3876-4a25-1ebb-bf3e7a81c700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"958\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"13\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/5d903e8d-4474-4cbf-8dd6-c9e3cc3c5b97/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <img alt=\"image.png\" data-imgfileid=\"503471306\" data-ratio=\"0.22540983606557377\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4bb89c5f-4e00-4e8a-b62f-065c26574900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"976\" data-original-style=\"null\" data-index=\"14\" src=\"https://image.jiqizhixin.com/uploads/editor/9459b4a8-b26e-4e11-94aa-8761ebbb6ee0/640.png\" data-fail=\"0\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" style=\"width: 70%;\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   Perplexity Deep Research 效果到底如何，欢迎大家评论区留言使用后的感受。\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>参考链接：</sup></em>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <sup><em>https://x.com/howie_serious/status/1890585920577102139</em></sup>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <sup><em>https://www.perplexity.ai/hub/blog/introducing-perplexity-deep-research</em></sup>\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <em><sup>https://x.com/dotey/status/1890537979573059696</sup></em>\n  </section>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Perplexity 推出免费 Deep Research 功能，通过 AI 快速生成深度研究报告，但在信息准确性和报告质量方面用户评价存在争议。",
